snippet.title: relaxdaily
snippet.description:
Hi, I'm Michael. I create calm piano music and relaxing music for your study, focus, creativity, or stress-release music playlist. I love composing, recording, and producing the relaxdaily music series since 2011. 

I also enjoy exploring beautiful nature spots and I capture the most inspiring ones on camera to share the views with you here in my music videos. My vision is to create calming and peaceful music for the mind and the heart, with the power to inspire, to heal, to help focus, to think better, clearer, and in new ways. For a better us, for a better planet.

Thank you so much for tuning in.
May your life unfold beautifully!
Michael 

You can help to keep relaxdaily alive here: patreon.com/relaxdaily 
Responsible for this channel's content: relaxdaily.net/legal
